<materialsCitation id="61F1F00F1B0AFFC6FD49FADEFBF5F8CB" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3798388366" pageId="20" pageNumber="531">“Chumbicha, Catamarca,” Departamento Capayan, Catamarca Province, 28°52’ S, 66°14’ W, 415 m, Argentina.</materialsCitation>
